imdb.plot outline: In the year 2030 NASA began a mission to discover what lies beyond our Galaxy, in hopes of creating a new world. Preparing to travel over 1000 yrs. into space, NASA selected the most elite human specimens to fulfill this mission. Over time, the ships population deteriorated rapidly until only four crew remain. These four characters begin to discover the ship's secret past, the truth behind their mission, and that they are not alone. In fact, they're not even human. CYCLE 14 was a finalist for SUNDANCE EPISODIC LAB 2017 as well as the New York TELEVISION FESTIVAL 2017.
